<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />不管到了幾歲，<delay20 />
在下雪的日子裡散步，
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是很讓人雀躍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道下雪了很讓人開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但你走路也要小心，
不要滑倒了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得我們今天很常見到面呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />外面天氣很冷，<delay8 />
記得散步要穿暖一點喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然天氣有點冷，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是下雪的日子<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總會讓人想出門走走呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天真的好冷喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次下雪<delay20 />我都會猶豫
要不要撐傘呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
</msbt>